    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "c0b52c50_ede1e71e",
        "filename": "tokenserver/appengine/impl/projectscope/config.go",
        "patchSetId": 16
      },
      "lineNbr": 105,
      "author": {
        "id": 1002539
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-03-08T02:45:08Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "why do this instead of just directly using cfgclient API in fetchConfigs?\n\nif err :\u003d cfgclient.Get(c, cfgclient.AsService, configSet, projectsCfg, textproto.Message(cfg), nil); err !\u003d nil {\n  return err\n}\n\nIt is not significantly more code.\n\nCoupling with policy.Policy is absolutely unnecessary here. This package should not use \u0027policy\u0027 package at all. \u0027policy\u0027 implements a logic of ingesting a policy document, and keeping it hot in memory to quickly answer questions. Project scoped accounts do not need that, they use datastore to answer questions. \u0027policy\u0027 is wrong tool here, and it should not be bended into solving the problem is wasn\u0027t supposed to be solving.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 105,
        "startChar": 19,
        "endLine": 105,
        "endChar": 39
      },
      "revId": "d5b6d82e5ad82bef55036c06b2094a0e6685f698",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "09b55e57_6e597435",
        "filename": "tokenserver/appengine/impl/projectscope/config.go",
        "patchSetId": 16
      },
      "lineNbr": 105,
      "author": {
        "id": 1307247
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-03-08T23:39:35Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t see a dependency on policy.Policy. The intention is to use LuciConfigFetcher as an abstraction to fetch LUCI configs. It\u0027s currently located under the policy package which I think we should refactor but this is a separate issue.\n\nHence I\u0027d like to use LuciConfigFetcher here and rather not call cfgclient.Get directly from multiple places.",
      "parentUuid": "c0b52c50_ede1e71e",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 105,
        "startChar": 19,
        "endLine": 105,
        "endChar": 39
      },
      "revId": "d5b6d82e5ad82bef55036c06b2094a0e6685f698",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
